data.description: Motivated Sellers - Bring Offers!  Welcome to this Custom Built All Brick Pool Home with 4 Bedrooms and 3 Full Baths.  Walking up to the front door, you are greeted by a Tiled front porch and glass door.  The foyer and great room have soaring 10ft ceilings with recessed lighting and crown molding.  Open concept Split floorplan with luxury wood look tile throughout, no carpet anywhere.  The Eat in kitchen is perfect for entertaining with breakfast bar, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.  The Owner's suite has a trey ceiling with large walk in closet.  The Spacious en suite bath has double vanities and walk in shower with glass door.  French doors from the Great Room lead out onto the covered porch and into the backyard oasis with a Gunite Saltwater Pool, paver patio, and tropical landscaping.  Yard has a Sprinkler well and pump with timer for care free watering.  Separate laundry room with door to the double car garage with professionally applied epoxy flooring.  This move in ready home is just a Short drive to the sugar white sand of Navarre Beach and close to shopping and restaurants.  When you already live in paradise, where will you go on vacation?  Book your tour today! Seller is offering $10,000 in closing cost assistance with full price offer.
